title: Preview Another New Real Estate Song “Two Arrows”
text: Real Estate are releasing a new album next month, In Mind, which they announced last week with lead single " Darling ." Bandleader Martin Courtney recently sat down for an interview with NPR , and host Bob Boilen played a bit of a 7-minute-long song that's featured on the album called "Two Arrows."
